The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-31-2013 THURS





The Glenn Beck Program




      


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 10/31/13Thursday, October 31, 2013 10:52 AM


The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,




It's a special Halloween edition of the program complete with staffers in costume and
 a lesson on the history of Halloween.

  Also, live dramatic readings of the true master of horror, Edgar Allen Poe.

  Plus, Ann Coulter, joins the show to discuss the latest on the Obamacare debacle.
